import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-navbar', templateUrl: './navbar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./navbar.component.css'] }) export class NavbarComponent { isMenuOpen = false; constructor(private router: Router) {} toggleMenu() { this.isMenuOpen = !this.isMenuOpen; } isActive(route: string): boolean { return this.router.url === route; } }
